>> Sreenivasan: ON THIS EDITION

00:12.045 --> 00:14.047
FOR SUNDAY, DECEMBER 28:

00:14.047 --> 00:15.315
A COMMERCIAL AIRLINER CARRYING

00:15.315 --> 00:16.884
162 PEOPLE VANISHES IN SOUTHEAST

00:16.884 --> 00:18.285
ASIA.

00:18.285 --> 00:19.219
WE'LL HAVE THE LATEST ON THE

00:19.219 --> 00:20.387
SEARCH.

