>> WE DON'T KNOW WHAT HAPPENED

00:21.421 --> 00:22.823
YET, SO WE'LL WAIT FOR THE

00:22.823 --> 00:24.825
ACCIDENT INVESTIGATION.

00:24.825 --> 00:26.059
>> Sreenivasan: THE CHRISTMAS

00:26.059 --> 00:27.094
SHOPPING SEASON DRAWS TO A

00:27.094 --> 00:28.095
CLOSE.

