HOW DID RETAILERS ACROSS THE

00:29.062 --> 00:30.631
NATION DO?

00:30.631 --> 00:32.466
AND IN OUR SIGNATURE SEGMENT,

00:32.466 --> 00:33.767
PEOPLE BEING SENT TO JAIL

00:33.767 --> 00:35.602
BECAUSE THEY CAN'T PAY FINES.

00:35.602 --> 00:36.904
MANY EXPERTS BELIEVE IT'S

00:36.904 --> 00:38.639
UNCONSTITUTIONAL.

