HARDER, BUT AS THE OLD SAYING

00:44.611 --> 00:46.079
GOES, YOU KNOW YOU CAN'T SQUEEZE

00:46.079 --> 00:47.614
BLOOD FROM A TURNIP.

00:47.614 --> 00:48.649
>> Sreenivasan: NEXT ON PBS

