ITALIAN AND GREEK HELICOPTER

03:45.859 --> 03:47.227
CREWS ARE AIRLIFTING PASSENGERS

03:47.227 --> 03:48.428
OFF THE VESSEL, DESPITE HEAVY

03:48.428 --> 03:50.097
RAIN AND STRONG WINDS IN THE

03:50.097 --> 03:51.064
AREA.

03:51.064 --> 03:52.165
A GREEK GOVERNMENT OFFICIAL SAID

03:52.165 --> 03:54.367
ONE MAN WAS CONFIRMED DEAD.

03:54.367 --> 03:56.002
THE INTERNATIONAL COMBAT MISSION

03:56.002 --> 03:57.104
IN AFGHANISTAN FORMALLY ENDED

03:57.104 --> 03:59.139
TODAY, MORE THAN 13 YEARS AFTER

03:59.139 --> 04:00.207
IT BEGAN IN THE AFTERMATH OF

04:00.207 --> 04:02.776
9/11.

04:02.776 --> 04:04.444
SUNDAY'S CEREMONY PUTS AFGHAN

04:04.444 --> 04:06.213
FORCES OFFICIALLY IN CHARGE OF

04:06.213 --> 04:07.514
THE ONGOING BATTLE AGAINST THE

04:07.514 --> 04:09.049
TALIBAN.

04:09.049 --> 04:11.084
EVEN SO, NEARLY 11,000 AMERICAN

04:11.084 --> 04:12.652
MILITARY PERSONNEL WILL REMAIN

04:12.652 --> 04:13.687
TO ASSIST THE AFGHAN ARMY AND

04:13.687 --> 04:14.621
POLICE.

04:14.621 --> 04:16.056
MORE THAN 2,000 AMERICANS HAVE

04:16.056 --> 04:17.257
DIED IN THE CONFLICT.

04:17.257 --> 04:18.692
ISLAMIC STATE FIGHTERS

04:18.692 --> 04:19.826
REPORTEDLY HAVE KILLED NEARLY 12

04:19.826 --> 04:20.727
HUNDRED SYRIAN CIVILIANS DURING

04:20.727 --> 04:23.096
THE PAST SIX MONTHS.

04:23.096 --> 04:24.631
THIS ACCORDING TO THE SYRIAN

04:24.631 --> 04:26.032
OBSERVATORY FOR HUMAN RIGHTS.

