THE GROUP SAYS ISIS ALSO HAS

04:28.668 --> 04:30.437
KILLED 120 OF ITS OWN MEMBERS,

04:30.437 --> 04:32.239
MOST OF THEM FOREIGN FIGHTERS

04:32.239 --> 04:34.574
WHO WERE SEEKING TO RETURN HOME.

