U.S.-LED AIRSTRIKES CONTINUED

04:36.042 --> 04:37.210
AGAINST ISIS TARGETS IN SYRIA

04:37.210 --> 04:39.746
AND IRAQ TODAY.

04:39.746 --> 04:41.314
IN A TELEVISION INTERVIEW TODAY,

04:41.314 --> 04:42.582
THE U.S. EBOLA RESPONSE

04:42.582 --> 04:43.717
COORDINATOR OFFERED AN UPDATE

04:43.717 --> 04:44.751
ABOUT THE FIGHT AGAINST THE

04:44.751 --> 04:46.453
DISEASE.

04:46.453 --> 04:47.754
>> I THINK YOU HAVE TO SEPARATE

04:47.754 --> 04:49.422
WHERE WE HERE AT HOME FROM WEST

04:49.422 --> 04:50.724
AFRICA.

04:50.724 --> 04:52.025
HERE AT HOME WE HAVE MADE

04:52.025 --> 04:53.326
SIGNIFICANT STRIDES TO PREPARE

04:53.326 --> 04:54.227
FOR THE OCCASIONAL CASE OF EBOLA

04:54.227 --> 04:55.228
THAT WE'LL SEE FROM TIME TO TIME

04:55.228 --> 04:56.830
ON OUR SHORES.

