CASES A DAY TO DOWN TO FIVE-TO-

05:02.435 --> 05:03.937
TEN NEW CASES A DAY, BUT THERE'S

05:03.937 --> 05:04.905
STILL A LOT OF WORK TO BE DONE

05:04.905 --> 05:05.839
IN SIERRA LEONE AND TROUBLING

05:05.839 --> 05:09.309
SIGNS IN GUINEA.

05:09.309 --> 05:11.178
SO I THINK WE'RE NEARING A PIVOT

05:11.178 --> 05:13.213
POINT IN THIS WHERE THE NUMBER

05:13.213 --> 05:15.215
OF NEW CASES OVER IN WEST AFRICA

05:15.215 --> 05:16.650
HAVE STABILIZED BUT THIS WON'T

05:16.650 --> 05:18.718
BE DONE UNTIL WE GET ALL THE WAY

05:18.718 --> 05:21.421
TO ZERO.

05:21.421 --> 05:22.756
IT'S LIKE A FOREST FIRE, A FEW

05:22.756 --> 05:24.457
EMBERS BURNING AND THE THING CAN

05:24.457 --> 05:29.095
REIGNITE ANY TIME.

05:29.095 --> 05:30.063
>> Sreenivasan: AND DOCTORS IN

05:30.063 --> 05:30.897
HOUSTON SAY FORMER PRESIDENT

05:30.897 --> 05:31.865
GEORGE H.W. BUSH'S CONDITION IS

05:31.865 --> 05:32.899
IMPROVING.

