HE WAS TAKEN BY AMBULANCE TO THE

05:33.900 --> 05:35.602
HOSPITAL TUESDAY AFTER

05:35.602 --> 05:36.469
COMPLAINING OF SHORTNESS OF

05:36.469 --> 05:37.304
BREATH.

