JAILED BECAUSE THEY COULDN'T

06:03.697 --> 06:04.631
AFFORD TO PAY THEIR FINES.

06:04.631 --> 06:05.665
CRITICS SAY THE PRACTICE IS

06:05.665 --> 06:09.636
TANTAMOUNT TO THE RESTORATION OF

